1999-04-11  Andreas J. Koenig  <andreas.koenig@anima.de>

	* Improved the query-unmask handler to work with escaped requests
	from non-compliant pre-1.1 proxies.

	* Added the amazon link to the references.

1999-04-07  Andreas J. Koenig  <andreas.koenig@anima.de>

	* Added Eric Cholet's recipe how to disable caching in the major
	browsers which tend to have broken behaviour.

	* Added this ChangeLog and Makefile.PL to make the document a
	standalone distribution until it settles and becomes stable.
 
	* Added description of no_cache() by Frank Cringle.

	* Added note about Content-Type being sent anyway by Frank
	Cringle.

	* Added "Avoiding" chapter written by Frank Cringle

1999-04-06  Andreas J. Koenig  <andreas.koenig@anima.de>

	* Made a few stylistic changes suggested by Tom Hukins.

	* Removed the wrong comment about the speed of the time utilities.

	* Changed several citations that were taken from RFC 2068, because
	they changed in the current draft.

	* Changed the reference to HTTP/1.1 as Wham Bang pointed out to me
	that there is a draft "06" that replaces the RFC.

1999-04-05  Andreas J. Koenig  <andreas.koenig@anima.de>
	
	* Changed the code examples to use Apache::File where appropriate

	* Added Cache-Control max-age

	* added a long chapter on ETag

	* added a comment about "?" in requests and a handler to work around

	* lots of small additions

1999-03-30  Andreas J. Koenig  <andreas.koenig@anima.de>

	* First version posted as mail to the mod_perl mailing list
